// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2286 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: f094dc29-763a-563d-b1af-081895afdc18

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
